This paper is most likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and specifically machine translation. The use of a hierarchical char2word encoder also suggests that it may fall under the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves a neural network model. Additionally, the paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of a neural network for language processing. Finally, the paper may also be relevant to the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it involves the use of attention plots, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks.
